OL,3,COfsted to keep single-phrase ratings
OL,4,Cdespite calls to axe them
OL,6,FIt said its priority is to look for
OL,7,Fways to improve the inspection system
OL,8,Frather than "developing an alternative
OL,9,Fto it".
OL,11,FThe Government's response has been
OL,12,Fdescribed by education union leaders
OL,13,Fas "deeply disappointing" and a missed
OL,14,Fopportunity for "meaningful change".
OL,16,FProfessor Julia Waters, the sister of
OL,17,FMrs Perry, called the response
OL,18,F"woefully inadequate" and said the
OL,19,Fchanges offered do not go "far enough".
