OL,3,COfsted to keep single-phrase ratings
OL,4,Cdespite calls to axe them
OL,6,FThe inspectorate has come under
OL,7,Fgreater scrutiny in the past year
OL,8,Fafter the suicide of Mrs Perry.
OL,10,FThe headteacher took her own life
OL,11,Fafter an Ofsted report downgraded her
OL,12,FCaversham Primary School in Reading
OL,13,Ffrom its highest rating,
OL,14,F"outstanding", to its lowest rating,
OL,15,F"inadequate", over safeguarding
OL,16,Fconcerns.
OL,18,FIn December, a coroner concluded the
OL,19,FOfsted inspection on November 15-16 in
OL,20,F2022 "contributed" to Mrs Perry's
OL,21,Fdeath.
