OL,3,COfsted to keep single-phrase ratings
OL,4,Cdespite calls to axe them
OL,6,FA report by the Education Select
OL,7,FCommittee in January called on the DfE
OL,8,Fand Ofsted to develop an alternative
OL,9,Fto the single-word judgments "as a
OL,10,Fpriority" to better capture the
OL,11,F"complex nature of a school's
OL,12,Fperformance".
OL,14,FIt said as a "first step" the websites
OL,15,Fof Ofsted and the DfE should show a
OL,16,Fschool's rating in different areas,
OL,17,Fnot just the overall judgment.
OL,19,FThe DfE listed the benefits of one-
OL,20,Fword judgments in its response to MPs.
OL,26,@qD@^OUrD@IO]sD@AOUtD@LO]vD@NOUvD@YO]
