OL,3,COfsted to keep single-phrase ratings
OL,4,Cdespite calls to axe them
OL,6,FIt said: "So, while the Government
OL,7,Fwill continue to listen to views and
OL,8,Flook at alternative systems, including
OL,9,Fthe various approaches taken
OL,10,Finternationally, the Government's view
OL,11,Fis that there are significant benefits
OL,12,Ffrom having an Ofsted overall
OL,13,Feffectiveness grade.
OL,15,F"In our view the priority is to look
OL,16,Ffor ways to improve the current system
OL,17,Frather than developing an alternative
OL,18,Fto it.
OL,26,@nD@JOUwD@AOU
