OL,3,COfsted to keep single-phrase ratings
OL,4,Cdespite calls to axe them
OL,6,F"This includes considering with Ofsted
OL,7,Fthe presentation of its findings and
OL,8,Fgrades, and opportunities to highlight
OL,9,Fsome of the detail sitting under the
OL,10,Fsummary grade."
OL,12,FThe DfE added that it agreed with the
OL,13,Fcross-party group that part of this is
OL,14,Fabout "increasing visibility" of the
OL,15,Fgraded sub-judgments that Ofsted makes
OL,16,F` such as "quality of education" and
OL,17,F"behaviour and attitudes".
