OL,3,COfsted to keep single-phrase ratings
OL,4,Cdespite calls to axe them
OL,6,FProf Waters, Mrs Perry's sister, said:
OL,7,F"It is depressing to see the
OL,8,FGovernment still defending aspects of
OL,9,Fthe inspection system, such as single-
OL,10,Fword judgements, that are so harmful,
OL,11,Fdivisive and counter-productive."
OL,13,FShe added: "The Government's response
OL,14,Fto the Education Committee's report on
OL,15,FOfsted is woefully inadequate.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@aO]uD@LOU
