OL,3,COfsted to keep single-phrase ratings
OL,4,Cdespite calls to axe them
OL,6,F"It is very difficult for me and my
OL,7,Ffamily to see the Government refer to
OL,8,Fmy sister by name, and then so clearly
OL,9,Ffail to respond to the many important
OL,10,Flessons from her death, that the
OL,11,Fcoroner and the Education Committee
OL,12,Fhave raised."
OL,14,F"The small tweaks to the current,
OL,15,Fdangerous system that have so far been
OL,16,Foffered do not go anywhere near far
OL,17,Fenough. We need to see urgent, root-
OL,18,Fand-branch reform of this fatally
OL,19,Fflawed inspection system," she added.
