OL,3,COfsted to keep single-phrase ratings
OL,4,Cdespite calls to axe them
OL,6,FHe said the DfE's response "smacks of
OL,7,Fa government that is out of touch with
OL,8,Fparents and professionals alike."
OL,10,FMr Whiteman added: "The government's
OL,11,Fdefence of discredited, simplistic,
OL,12,Fand reductive single-word or phrase
OL,13,Fjudgements simply perpetuates an
OL,14,Finhumane and unreliable inspection
OL,15,Fsystem that is driving a mental health
OL,16,Fand wellbeing crisis across England's
OL,17,Fschools."
OL,26,@nD@\OUpD@aO]rD@TOUyD@IO]
