OL,4,Cdespite calls to axe them
OL,6,FPepe Di'Iasio, general secretary of
OL,7,Fthe Association of School and College
OL,8,FLeaders (ASCL), said: "The
OL,9,FGovernment's response to the call for
OL,10,Fan alternative to single-phrase
OL,11,Fjudgments is deeply disappointing.
OL,13,F"Its solution is to 'consider' the
OL,14,Fpresentation of Ofsted reports rather
OL,15,Fthan the system itself.
OL,26,@pD@WOUuD@AOU
