OL,3,COfsted to keep single-phrase ratings
OL,4,Cdespite calls to axe them
OL,6,FConservative MP Robin Walker, chairman
OL,7,Fof the Education Select Committee,
OL,8,Fsaid: "In recent months we have seen
OL,9,Fencouraging signs that the
OL,10,Finspectorate has listened and is
OL,11,Fwilling to change.
OL,13,F"It is especially welcome to hear from
OL,14,FDfE that it is open to ideas about how
OL,15,Fthe single-word judgments system could
OL,16,Fbe improved upon ` a set of policies
OL,17,Fthat the Government alone has the
OL,18,Fauthority to change.
OL,26,@pD@GOUuD@AOU
