OL,3,COfsted to keep single-phrase ratings
OL,4,Cdespite calls to axe them
OL,6,F"My committee agrees that there are
OL,7,Fbenefits to having a system of
OL,8,Fjudgments or ratings, such as the
OL,9,Fclarity they provide for parents.
OL,11,F"But we also maintain that a more
OL,12,Fnuanced version of this system is both
OL,13,Fachievable and in everyone's
OL,14,Finterests."
OL,16,FAn Ofsted spokesman said: "Ofsted aims
OL,17,Falways to be a force for good in this
OL,18,Fcountry, ensuring schools, children's
OL,19,Fhomes, nurseries and colleges deliver
OL,20,Fthe highest standards of education and
OL,21,Fcare to children.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUvD@KO]xD@[OU
