OL,4,Cdespite calls to axe them
OL,6,F"But we know we can improve. That is
OL,7,Fwhy we launched the Big Listen, which
OL,8,Finvites feedback from parents,
OL,9,Fprofessionals and children on
OL,10,Feverything we do."
OL,12,FA DfE spokesperson said: "We have no
OL,13,Fplans to remove one-word judgments.
OL,14,FThey give parents the confidence in
OL,15,Fchoosing the right school for their
OL,16,Fchild and provide a clear basis for
OL,17,Ftaking action to improve
OL,18,Funderperforming schools.
